data.description: Corner House with Spectacular Pond View. New Roof , Renovated Porcelain Floor , Renovated Bathroom and Fruit trees .     Looking for your own piece of paradise? The Oaks is a GOLFERS paradise conveniently located to schools, medical facilities, Lake Toho for world class bass fishing, theme parks, airport, shopping & restaurants! LOCATION: across from the 12th tee box on the pond. UNIQUE, decorative tile entry. Inside INCREDIBLE first & lasting impressions, you will be greeted by Four Seasons style stunning comfort & views. Romantic crash-pad or PEACEFUL COTTAGE? ABSOLUTELY. Recharge, refresh, quick shower & back in the game! Fabulous flow for entertaining yet quietly enveloping for daily living. Entertaining-sized rooms to watch the game & enjoy family time, just sit down & relax. Join the party? Sleep? Both? YES. Functional & efficient, split bedroom design. A perfect retreat to enjoy with family & friends. ENJOY lunch in the kitchen or on the screened lanai. The Owners & their family wanted the vacation lifestyle The Oaks offers, & the much loved Florida Sunshine. BOTH peaceful golf & pond setting, the year round “open-air” living style with exclusive views of natural landscaped areas is what attracted them. Original owner & never rented, the home can be used as investment property. Enjoy your down time this one’s done with upgraded doors, patio tile and fresh paint. BRAND NEW GRANITE KITCHEN COUNTERS, faucet & sink, even down to the knobs. Bring your bike, walking shoes, and Uber app, & move right in! This can be Your Florida Getaway. Come look inside today to see all the Beauty, Warmth and Value this home has to offer.
